        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Federal Small Businesses Contractor Prompt Payment Reporting Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires each federal agency to report to Congress on the timeliness, including acceleration, of payments made to a prime contractor that is a small business or that subcontracts with a small business.</p>]]></text>
